racteris- tics,\u201d QEH Working Paper Series \u2013 QEHWPS 123, University of Oxford. 39 Liu, L., Chow, K., and U. Li (2006), \u201cDeterminants of Foreign Direct Investment in East Asia: Did China Crowd Out FDI from Her Developing East Asian Neighbours,\u201d Working Paper, No. 617, Hong Kong Monetary Authority. Memi\u015f, E. and M. F. Montes (2005), \u201cPeople, Trade, and Development: Learning from Asia-Pacific,\u201d Policy Paper, UNDP Regional Centre in Colombo (Dec.).", "start_char_idx": null, "end_char_idx": null, "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_seperator": "\n"}, "__type__": "1"}, "dea1ac2e-0351-4a8f-96bf-969316c9d224": {"__data__": {"id_": "dea1ac2e-0351-4a8f-96bf-969316c9d224", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/potential-cooperative-regional-industrial-development-strategies-asia-and-implications-emerging-china-and-india", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "The Potential for Cooperative Regional Industrial Development Strategies in Asia and the Implications of Emerging China and India", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/potential-cooperative-regional-industrial-development-strategies-asia-and-implications-emerging-china-and-india", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "hash": "b5813be28d2c9d186fc2fd8bbe8c00d1348f8f919eeb43616b3d4f5d07e74f69"}, "2": {"node_id": "81f14c74-e350-4c69-b57d-d37790d867fe", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/potential-cooperative-regional-industrial-development-strategies-asia-and-implications-emerging-china-and-india