f59b", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/trade-environmental-and-energy-services-and-human-development", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "hash": "2825d86687a4d99a07f1fffb0e2c518e7ba81091bc70b3e340a396a0cda952d5"}}, "hash": "7d34b3c10e9c48cf24acd12665896549281716d7f9bf7ba7bd3c24ab450d163c", "text": "5 Acronyms and Abbreviations ADB Asian Development Bank ADR American Depository Receipt AEP Asia Environmental Partnership ASEAN Association of South East Asian Nations BBC British Broadcasting Corporation BIT Bilateral Trade Agreement BOO Build Operate Own BOT Build Operate Transfer BOOT Build Operate Own Transfer CDIAC Carbon Dioxide Information Analysis Center CD-ROM Compact Disk Read-Only Memory CFC Chloro Fluoro Carbons CIEL Center for International Environmental Law CGN Compressed Natural Gas DC District of Columbia EC European Community EU European Union FDI Foreign Direct Investment GATS General Agreement on Trade in Services GATT General Agreement on Tariff and Trade GDP Gross Domestic Product GENCO General Environmental Conservation Company (Thailand) HDI Human Development Index IEA International Energy Agency IPP Independent Power Producers ISO International Organization for Standardization KWSB Karachi Water and Sanitation Board LDC Least Developed Country LICSU Low-Income Consumer Support Unit LPG Liquefied Petroleum Gas MBI Market-Based Instrument MDG Millennium Development Goals 6 | Trade in Environmental and Energy Services and Human Development: Contributing to Well-Being, Growth and Access for All MFN Most Favoured Nation MTOE Million Tonnes of Oil Equivalent MW Mega Watt NGO Non-Governmental Organization NT National Treatment ODA Official Development Assistance OECD Organization for Economic Cooperation and Development OPEC Organization of the Petroleum Exporting Countries OPP Orangi Pilot Project PDR Peopl